node.text:
Our 12 Days of Giving starts now! We’re kicking off the giving by helping you bring the essence of Pure Salt to your home this holiday season! Like with any of our projects, that means leaning in to design that is cozy, fresh, clean (in every sense), and inspired to create a natural atmosphere where cherished memories are made. We think every home needs a little bit of:
- cozy music
- candles & scents
- calm & clean decor
- candles, candles, and more candles!
Check out our stories today to learn more about how we use each element to infuse the season with some Pure Salt magic ✨// 🎬: @trevorfilm

node.text: Dipping our toes into video content with @618studios to tell you a little bit more about who we are and what makes us Pure Salt!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Pure Salt Interiors in Newport Beach, California. May be an image of sofa and living room.

node.text: This cozy view of our #portstreetsproject living room is everything✨ our elm coffee table and vintage rug add great texture, our sectional and stacks of fave shoppe pillows bring in the softness, and all the pops of greenery make the space feel so lively! // 📷: @vlentine

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Pure Salt Interiors in Rancho Mission Viejo. May be an image of furniture and bedroom.

node.text: Getting a dreamy bedroom looks is easy when you follow our bedding essentials checklist! Add one of our reversible duvets for double the possibilities, stack some of our go-to pillows, and add calming decor and lighting for ambiance✨check out everything you need to know on stories this afternoon, plus our step by step guide on how to make a Pure Salt bed on Grain of Salt! // 📷: @vlentine

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Pure Salt Interiors in Los Gatos, California with @littlesaltshoppe. May be an image of indoor.

node.text:
No Sunday scaries here 🙅‍♀️ just sunny desk views as we gear up for this amazing week ahead and our littles jump into a brand new school year✨ ⁣
⁣
That being said, happy back to school to all the mamas out there! We're sending all our hopes and wishes for a great year for our kiddos // 📷: @vlentine

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Pure Salt Interiors on August 14, 2021 tagging @hannahbrown. May be an image of bedroom.

node.text:
Another reason to fall in love with our new bedding collection? All the duvets are reversible! We love having options when styling a space, and no room changes as much as our bedrooms—we need things to always feel fresh and new! Seen here in #hannahshouseproject our Cliffside duvet has a subtle, pretty pinstripe on one side, and the coziest taupe on the other. We love it when we can have the best of both worlds✨ // 📷: @vlentine

Our bedding collection was created with comfort and style at the forefront of our minds, utilizes texture and a natural palette to bring cozy interest to every bedroom. Ranging from basics, like super soft sheets, to elegant extras, like our waffle knit throws, this collection lends itself to a layered look, wrapping your bed and you in cozy warmth and lovely, lived-in style // 📷: @vlentine⁣

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Pure Salt Interiors in Newport Beach, California. May be an image of furniture and bedroom.

node.text:
Today we are falling in love and into bed with our new bedding collection ✨ bedrooms are the most personal and intimate rooms of our homes—they are where we get our rest, where we reconnect and recharge, and they need to feel like a retreat away from the hectic world around us. We wanted to create something that felt fresh and that you could continually refresh with different pairings and layers, so we designed a reversible duvet in three colorways to suit every mood, season, and style. We think with the possibility of this many looks, you are sure to fall in love and into bed // 📷: @vlentine⁣
⁣
⁣

node.text: Talk about a dream come true! We have exciting news and can’t contain ourselves any longer—we have quite literally been dreaming of this since we founded Pure Salt—we are thrilled to say that our long await bedding collection is finally here! And it will be launching this Wednesday! If you know us and Pure Salt you know cozy comfy and beautiful go hand in hand as our design point of view, and these bedding pieces are so soft and so unique, we hope you love them as much as we do 🤍 // 📷: @vlentine
